*German: [[Brut]] {{f}}
{{mid}}
{{bottom}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To keep an [[egg]] [[warm]] to make it [[hatch]].
# To [[dwell]] upon [[moodily]] and [[at length]].
#to protect
#:''He sat '''brooding''' about the upcoming battle, fearing the outcome.''

